Title: Bicep Curl
SubTitle: Classic arm-building exercise
Description: A weight training exercise that targets the biceps brachii muscle. Stand or sit holding a dumbbell in each hand with an underhand grip.

Title: Plank
SubTitle: Isometric core strength exercise
Description: An isometric core strength exercise that involves maintaining a position similar to a push-up for the maximum possible time.

Title: Glute Bridges
SubTitle: Strengthens glutes and hamstrings
Description: Lie on your back with your knees bent and feet flat on the floor. Lift your hips off the floor until your knees, hips and shoulders form a straight line.
